---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nos Activités - UDTL 31">
	<!-- Main Header / Hero Section -->
	<header class="relative pt-40 pb-20 overflow-hidden min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-black/60">
			<!-- Background image replaced with simple inline styles for now, can be optimized later with Astro image -->
			<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888086425-d81bb19240f5?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Construction and action" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 mix-blend-multiply lg:object-center object-right" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,1) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,1) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%);"/>
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background/60"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 w-full">
			<div class="max-w-3xl">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
					 <span class="w-12 h-1 bg-primary"></span>
					 <span class="font-headline font-bold text-xs tracking-widest text-primary uppercase">Sur le terrain</span>
				</div>
				
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black font-headline tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] text-on-background mb-8">
					NOS ACTIONS,<br>
					<span class="signature-gradient text-transparent bg-clip-text">VOS DROITS.</span>
				</h1>
				
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-body font-light text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12" style="text-wrap: balance;">
					Négociations salariales, défense juridique, et actions de protestation. Découvrez l'engagement quotidien de l'UDTL 31 pour faire valoir vos conditions de travail.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-24">
		<!-- Filters / Navigation -->
		<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-16 border-b border-outline-variant/30 pb-4">
			<button class="font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase border-b-2 border-primary text-primary pb-2 px-2 transition-colors">Toutes les actus</button>
			<button class="font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-background pb-2 px-2 transition-colors">Négociations</button>
			<button class="font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-background pb-2 px-2 transition-colors">Juridique</button>
			<button class="font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-background pb-2 px-2 transition-colors">Grèves & Mouvements</button>
		</div>

		<!-- The Editorial Feed -->
		<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 gap-y-16">
			<!-- Article Card 1 -->
			<article class="group bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
				<div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578575437130-527eed3abbec?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Réunion" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"/>
					<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container font-headline font-bold text-[10px] px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-widest rounded-[2px] shadow-sm">
						Négociation
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
					<div class="font-body text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">12 Octobre 2024</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline font-black text-2xl tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
						Revalorisation de 5% obtenue pour les chauffeurs routiers.
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
						Suite à trois jours de négociations intensives avec les instances patronales, l'UDTL 31 a arraché un accord historique concernant la grille tarifaire.
					</p>
					<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-headline font-bold text-[11px] text-on-background uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-on-background pb-1 w-fit group-hover:text-primary group-hover:border-primary transition-colors">
						Lire l'article complet <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Article Card 2 -->
			<article class="group bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
				<div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589578228468-ebce1ce6414f?q=80&w=1953&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Victoire juridique" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"/>
					<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container font-headline font-bold text-[10px] px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-widest rounded-[2px] shadow-sm">
						Action Juridique
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
					<div class="font-body text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">28 Septembre 2024</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline font-black text-2xl tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
						Victoire au Prud'hommes contre la société LogisExpress
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
						Le tribunal a statué en faveur de 12 salariés licenciés abusivement. La justice a reconnu les heures supplémentaires non payées sur les deux dernières années.
					</p>
					<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-headline font-bold text-[11px] text-on-background uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-on-background pb-1 w-fit group-hover:text-primary group-hover:border-primary transition-colors">
						Lire l'article complet <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Article Card 3 -->
			<article class="group bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
				<div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620005720977-1c43714cddcc?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Grève logistique" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"/>
					<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary text-on-primary font-headline font-bold text-[10px] px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-widest rounded-[2px] shadow-sm">
						Mouvement Social
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
					<div class="font-body text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">En cours</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline font-black text-2xl tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
						Préavis de grève illimitée pour la plateforme fret de Blagnac
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
						Face au refus de la direction d'adapter les rythmes de nuit et l'absence de prime de pénibilité, les équipes logistiques de Blagnac entament un mouvement dur.
					</p>
					<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-headline font-bold text-[11px] text-primary uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-primary pb-1 w-fit hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
						Suivre le mouvement <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Article Card 4 -->
			<article class="group bg-surface-container-low flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm overflow-hidden p-8 border-t-8 border-tertiary-container shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500">
				<div class="flex-grow">
					<div class="font-body text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Dossier Spécial</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline font-black text-2xl tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 group-hover:text-tertiary-container transition-colors">
						Analyse des risques TMS dans la branche livraison urbaine.
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8">
						Notre bureau d'étude publie les résultats d'une enquête sur six mois impliquant 300 coursiers et livreurs toulousains. Le bilan est alarmant concernant le matériel imposé.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
						 <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-on-background">
							 <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-[2px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">warning</span>
							 80% se plaignent du dos.
						 </li>
						 <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-on-background">
							 <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-[2px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">warning</span>
							 Véhicules utilitaires inadaptés.
						 </li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-headline font-bold text-[11px] text-on-background uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-on-background pb-1 w-fit group-hover:text-tertiary-container group-hover:border-tertiary-container transition-colors mt-auto">
					Télécharger le PDF <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">download</span>
				</a>
			</article>
			
			<!-- Article Card 5 -->
			<article class="group bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col h-full rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
				<div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502444330042-d1a1ddf9bb5b?q=80&w=2073&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Santé" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"/>
					<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container font-headline font-bold text-[10px] px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-widest rounded-[2px] shadow-sm">
						Négociation
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
					<div class="font-body text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">15 Août 2024</div>
					<h3 class="font-headline font-black text-2xl tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
						Nouveaux accords sur la mutuelle santé obligatoire.
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow">
						Meilleure prise en charge des frais dentaires et optiques pour tous les salariés de la branche logisique de la région Occitanie.
					</p>
					<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-headline font-bold text-[11px] text-on-background uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-on-background pb-1 w-fit group-hover:text-primary group-hover:border-primary transition-colors">
						Lire l'article complet <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</article>

			<!-- Newsletter / Engage Card -->
			<div class="signature-gradient text-on-primary p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm shadow-xl flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
				 <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl mb-6 text-on-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">mail</span>
				 <h3 class="font-headline font-black text-3xl tracking-tight leading-none mb-4">Ne manquez aucune action.</h3>
				 <p class="font-body text-sm text-on-primary/90 mb-8 max-w-sm">Abonnez-vous à notre lettre d'information hebdomadaire pour suivre nos luttes et l'évolution de vos droits syndicaux locaux.</p>
				 <form class="w-full relative">
					 <input type="email" placeholder="Votre adresse email" class="w-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white placeholder-white/50 rounded-sm font-body px-4 py-4 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:outline-none backdrop-blur-sm" required>
					 <button type="submit" class="absolute right-2 top-2 bottom-2 bg-on-primary text-primary font-headline font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase px-4 rounded-[2px] hover:bg-surface-dim transition-colors">
						 S'inscrire
					 </button>
				 </form>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pagination -->
		<div class="mt-20 flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
			 <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/50 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors rounded-[2px]">
				  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">chevron_left</span>
			 </button>
			 <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary text-on-primary font-headline font-bold text-xs rounded-[2px]">1</button>
			 <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/50 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors font-headline font-bold text-xs rounded-[2px]">2</button>
			 <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/50 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors font-headline font-bold text-xs rounded-[2px]">3</button>
			 <span class="px-2 text-on-surface-variant">...</span>
			 <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/50 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors font-headline font-bold text-xs rounded-[2px]">8</button>
			 <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/50 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors rounded-[2px]">
				  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">chevron_right</span>
			 </button>
		</div>
	</main>

	<!-- Unified Bottom CTA -->
	<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 mb-12">
		<div class="signature-gradient p-12 md:p-24 rounded-sm relative overflow-hidden text-center group">
			<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black font-headline tracking-tighter text-white mb-6">
					PLUS FORTS, ENSEMBLE.
				</h2>
				<p class="text-white/90 font-body text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
					La défense de vos droits ne se fera pas sans vous. Rejoignez les milliers de travailleurs qui construisent la logistique de demain dans la Haute-Garonne.
				</p>
				<a href="/adhesion" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-primary px-8 py-5 rounded-sm font-headline font-black text-sm tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] transform hover:-translate-y-1">
					Adhérer à l'UDTL 31
				</a>
			</div>
			<!-- Decorative abstract background forms indicating action -->
			<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] border border-white/10 rounded-full translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] border border-white/10 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 delay-100"></div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
